<h3 style="text-align: center; margin: auto 0cm 4.2pt; background: #efefed;" align="center"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; color: navy;">* Inventários</span></span></h3>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center; margin: auto 0cm 4.2pt; background: #efefed;" align="center"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; color: navy;">* Material gráfico</span></span></h3>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center; margin: auto 0cm 4.2pt; background: #efefed;" align="center"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; color: navy;">* Escolas</span></span></h3>
